th%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20her%20rival%2C%20Republican%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20are%20doing%20all%20they%20can%20to%20lure%20voters%20on%20Election%20Day%20Nov.%205%20and%20in%20early%20voting%20starting%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20part%2C%20Trump%20dismissed%20Swift's%20Tuesday%20night%20endorsement%20of%20Harris%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20Taylor%20fan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20voter%20registrations%20down%20among%20young%20people%20in%20a%20country%20where%2018%20is%20the%20voting%20age%2C%20the%20first%20challenge%20for%20either%20campaign%20may%20be%20getting%20them%20to%20register%20to%20vote%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoung%20voters%20played%20a%20decisive%20role%20in%20Democratic%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20victory%20over%20the%20then-incumbent%20Trump%20in%202020.%20Biden%20captured%20about%2061%25%20of%20the%20vote%20to%20Trump's%2036%25%20of%20voters%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2029%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Tufts%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20July%202024%20analysis%20by%20Tufts%20University's%20youth%20civic%20engagement%20group%2C%20CIRCLE%2C%20found%20that%20voter%20registrations%20have%20dropped%20significantly%20since%20then%20in%2036%20states%20among%20those%20aged%2018-29.%20Harris%20launched%20her%20campaign%20on%20July%2021%20after%20Biden%20withdrew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRegistering%20youths%20remains%20a%20major%20task%20in%20the%20months%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnter%20Swift%2C%20an%20artist%20so%20successful%20she%20tied%20hip-hop%20star%20Beyonce's%20record%20of%2030%20lifetime%20awards%20at%20the%20MTV%20Video%20Music%20Awards%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20A%202023%20Morning%20Consult%20poll%20found%20that%2055%25%20of%20self-described%20Swift%20fans%20were%20Democrats%20and%2045%25%20were%20millennials%20aged%2028%20to%2043.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20voting%20for%20%40kamalaharris%20because%20she%20fights%20for%20the%20rights%20and%20causes%20I%20believe%20need%20a%20warrior%20to%20champion%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Swift%20wrote%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20her%20284%20million%20Instagram%20followers%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20register%20to%20vote%20and%20make%20their%20own%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20post%20drew%2010.4%20million%20%26quot%3Blikes.%26quot%3B%20The%20vote.gov%20website%20received%20405%2C999%20visitors%20in%20the%2024%20hours%20after%20Swift%20shared%20a%20custom%20URL%20with%20followers%2C%20a%20U.S.%20government%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20aides%20say%20they%20would%20love%20for%20Swift%20to%20actively%20campaign%2C%20such%20as%20by%20appearing%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20her%20native%20Pennsylvania%2C%20a%20battleground%20state%20that%20could%20well%20decide%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20campaign%20itself%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20Swift's%20decision%20to%20back%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vice%20president's%20aides%20said%20they%20learned%20of%20Swift's%20support%20only%20when%20the%20entertainer%2C%2034%2C%20posted%20it%20on%20Instagram%20minutes%20after%20the%20vice%20president%20stepped%20off%20the%20debate%20stage%20in%20Philadelphia%20on%20Tuesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20QUESTION%20OF%20INFLUENCE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20difference%20does%20a%20celebrity%20endorsement%20make%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202008%20Northwestern%20University%20report%20found%20Oprah%20Winfrey's%20endorsement%20added%20a%20million%20votes%20to%20Barack%20Obama's%20tally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%202010%20North%20Carolina%20State%20University%20report%20found%20celebrity%20endorsements%20by%20George%20Clooney%20and%20Angelina%20Jolie%20did%20little%20to%20move%20the%20political%20needle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMargaretha%20Bentley%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Arizona%20State%20University%20whose%20class%20studies%20Swift's%20social%20importance%2C%20is%20unsure%