transfer%20business%20credit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%200%25%20intro%20APR%20if%20your%20company%20needs%20a%20financial%20lifeline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaigle%20also%20suggests%20contacting%C2%A0the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nfcc.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Foundation%20for%20Credit%20Counseling%3C%2Fa%3E%20(NFCC)%20to%20set%20up%20a%20debt%20management%20plan.%20This%20non-profit%20provides%20access%20to%20certified%20credit%20counselors%20who%20can%20help%20you%20set%20up%20a%20consistent%20monthly%20repayment%20amount.%20The%20NFCC%20also%20offers%20online%20courses%20in%20money%20management%20to%20boost%20your%20financial%20literacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUnderstand%20the%20true%20cost%20of%20high-interest%20debt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20gotten%20out%20of%20credit%20card%20debt%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20build%20healthy%20habits%20to%20ensure%20you%20stay%20out%20of%20debt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInterest%20rates%20make%20a%20real%20difference%2C%20and%20it's%20important%20to%20know%20what%20you're%20paying%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mark%20Elliot%2C%20chief%20customer%20officer%20of%20financial%20services%20company%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lendingclub.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELendingClub%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BMany%20consumers%20struggling%20with%20high-interest%20debt%20have%20expressed%20confusion%20surrounding%20credit%20card%20APRs%2C%20and%20credit%20card%20companies%20are%20happy%20to%20keep%20it%20that%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElliot%2C%20who%20has%20previous%20leadership%20experience%20at%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20and%20Capital%20One%2C%20also%20referenced%20a%20common%20misconception%20among%20everyday%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20consumers%20believe%20that%20making%20the%20minimum%20payment%20is%20an%20effective%20way%20to%20manage%20their%20credit%20card%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20Elliot%20said.%20However%2C%20he%20cautions%20that%20only%20paying%20the%20bare%20minimum%20on%20credit%20card%20balances%20can%20%26quot%3Blead%20to%20prolonged%20repayment%20periods%20and%20significantly%20more%20interest%20paid%20overtime.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20consumers%20struggling%20with%20high%20credit%20card%20debt%20should%20focus%20on%20developing%20financial%20literacy%20and%20stick%20with%20a%20spending%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20final%20word%20of%20advice%3A%20%26quot%3BDeveloping%20a%20repayment%20strategy%20is%20key%2C%26quot%3B%20Elliot%20said.%20%26quot%3BAim%20to%20pay%20more%20than%20the%20minimum%20payment%20to%20reduce%20the%20principal%20balance%20faster%2C%20and%20prioritize%20high-interest%20debt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cut-impact-credit-card-loan-rates-debt-consolidation-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726320902000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e36b42cfb7f307e571403e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cut-impact-credit-card-loan-rates-debt-consolidation-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Will%20the%20anticipated%20Federal%20Reserve%20rate%20cut%20help%20you%20escape%20high-interest%20debt%20more%20quickly%3F%20Financial%20experts%20say%20no%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20what%20to%20do%20instead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherinefan%40gmail.com%20(Katherine%20Fan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cut-impact-credit-card-loan-rates-debt-consolidation-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kartik%20and%20Triptii%20to%20star%20in%20Basu%E2%80%99s%20love%20story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726320784000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113352200%2Cimgsize-31744.cm