%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftianas-bayou-adventure-ride-magic-kingdom-disney-world-worth-it-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney%20rides%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20you%20want%20to%20prioritize.%20Once%20you%20choose%20your%20rides%2C%20the%20Disney%20app%20will%20offer%20you%20three%20one-hour-long%20slots%20(one%20for%20each%20ride).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20have%20three%20Lightning%20Lanes%20at%20once%20%E2%80%94%20that%20means%2C%20once%20you%20complete%20your%20first%20ride%2C%20you%20can%20add%20another%20one%20for%20later%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20every%20ride%20in%20the%20park%20is%20the%20same.%20Disney%20has%20already%20decided%20which%20rides%20are%20top-tier%2C%20and%20you%20can%20only%20book%20one%20top-tier%20ride%20at%20a%20time.%20The%20other%20two%20rides%20you%20can%20choose%20from%20have%20to%20be%20from%20the%20lower%20tier%20of%20rides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221976%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22little%20mermaid%20ride%20at%20magic%20kingdom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3c250955b01c3294cb13c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221484%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Little%20Mermaid%20is%20one%20of%20the%20lesser%20tier%20rides%2C%20according%20to%20Disney%20World.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20park's%20Lightning%20Lanes%20are%20differently%20priced%2C%20and%20they%20change%20depending%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20an%20upcoming%20Tuesday%20(the%20day%20of%20the%20week%20I%20went)%2C%20prices%20are%20as%20follows%3A%20%2427%20for%20Magic%20Kingdom%2C%20%2418%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffull-day-at-epcot-families-what-to-do-disney-world-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEpcot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%2422%20for%20Hollywood%20Studios%2C%20and%20%2416%20for%20Animal%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20opted%20for%20Hollywood%20Studios%2C%20since%20that%20had%20the%20most%20rides%20I%20wanted%20to%20experience.%20When%20I%20went%2C%20a%20Multi-Pass%20for%20Hollywood%20Studios%20was%20%2424.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20change%20with%20this%20new%20system%20is%20that%2C%20before%2C%20you%20were%20only%20able%20to%20schedule%20your%20Lightning%20Lanes%20on%20the%20day%20of%20your%20visit%20at%207%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20if%20you're%20staying%20at%20one%20of%20the%20resorts%20on%20Disney%20property%2C%20you%20can%20do%20it%20up%20to%20a%20week%20in%20advance.%20Everyone%20else%20can%20do%20it%20three%20days%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a501e16-dd84-45ee-8229-bbe0c2c33ca7%5C%22%3ESo%2C%20what's%20a%20Single%20Pass%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%20when%20I%20said%20some%20rides%20are%20top-tier%3F%20Well%2C%20some%20rides%20have%20been%20deemed%20even%20%3Cem%3Emore%20%3C%2Fem%3Eexclusive%20than%20those%20rides%2C%20and%20you%20can%20only%20purchase%20a%20Lightning%20Lane%20for%20those%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20rides%20around%20the%20parks%20%E2%80%94%20Seven%20Dwarfs%20Mine%20Train%2C%20TRON%20Lightcycle%2C%20Guardians%20of%20the%20Galaxy%3A%20Cosmic%20Rewind%2C%20Star%20Wars%3A%20Rise%20of%20the%20Resistance%2C%20and%20Avatar%20Flight%20of%20Passage%20%E2%80%94%20only%20have%20Lightning%20Lane%20Single%20Passes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20range%20from%20%2411%20to%20%2420%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20if%20you%20want%20to%20ensure%20you%20get%20on%20these%20rides%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20purchase%20an%20additional%20pass.%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20on%20TRON%2C%20which%20was%20another%20%2420.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221942%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20tron%20lightcycle%20at%20tomorrowland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3c1f25da406397bf3f883%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221444%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETRON%20Lightcycle%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20rides%20at%20Magic%20Kingdom.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20keeping%20track%2C%20that's%20a%20total%20of%20%2444%20in%20extras%2C%20for%20one%20person%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20my%20park-hopper%20ticket%2C%20which%20was%20%24247.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I%20spent%20%24291%20just%20to%20get%20into%20the%20park%20for%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d428ec19-a9c8-4c10-9922-2033c8e2009a%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20care%20about%20rides%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20necessary%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20additional%20fees%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20justify%20for%20a%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20paid%20for%20a%20single%20ticket%20for%20a%20single%20day%2C%20I'm%20grateful%20I%20opted%20for%20a%20Multi-Pass.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20breeze%20through%20all%20three%20rides%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20on%20at%20Hollywood%20Studios%2C%20and%20my%20wait%20for%20TRON%20was%20around%2010%20minutes.%20For%20perspective%2C%20the%20queues%20for%20popular%20rides%20can%20be%2075%20minutes%20and%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20pass%20meant%20I%20wasn't%20wasting%20precious%20park%20time%20in%20long%20lines%20and%20allowed%20me%20to%20pack%20much%20more%20into%20my%20day.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20I%20was%20going%20as%20part%20of%20a%20family%20of%20four%2C%20these%20passes%20would%20have%20cost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-genie-plus-skip-lines-worth-it-for-family-disneyland-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20extra%20%24176%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20just%20for%20one%20day.%20I%20can't%20even%20imagine%20how%20a%20family%20is%20supposed%20to%20do%20Lightning%20Lanes%20for%20multiple%20days%20at%20the%20parks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20just%20one%20way%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexpensive-things-that-used-to-be-free-at-disney-world-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20cost%20of%20going%20to%20Disney%20has%20increased%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20when%20FastPass%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%20the%20'90s%2C%20it%20was%20free%2C%20and%20it%20stayed%20that%20way%20for%20years.%20I%20remember%20going%20to%20Disney%20as%20a%20kid%20and%20receiving%20a%20physical%20printout%20that%20would%20tell%20you%20what%20time%20to%20come%20back%20so%20you%20could%20get%20on%20the%20shorter%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224746%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disney%20has%20started%20a%20FastPass%20ticket%20system%20for%20the%20popular%20Frozen%20Character%20Experience.%20What%20once%20took%20hours%20of%20waiting%20to%20visit%20with%20%26quot%3BFrozen%26quot%3B%20characters%20Elsa%20and%20Anna%20now%20takes%20minutes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e1d61ecfb7f307e57091d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223578%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20used%20to%20get%20an%20actual%20ticket%20to%20tell%20you%20when%20to%20come%20back.%3Cp%3ELeonard%20Ortiz%2FDigital%20First%20Media%2FOrange%20County%20Register%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20doing%20Disney%20on%20a%20budget%2C%20the%20Multi-Pass%20might%20not%20be%20for%20you%2C%20but%20I'd%20strongly%20recommend%20springing%20for%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20single%20rides.%20Those%20are%20the%20best%20attractions%20in%20the%20park%2C%20and%20you%20could%20waste%20hours%20trying%20to%20get%20on%20them%20without%20a%20Lightning%20Lane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you're%20already%20willing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-family-spent-10k-disney-world-trip-tips-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espend%20thousands%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20seems%20more%20and%20more%20likely%20these%20days%20%E2%80%94%20adding%20the%20Multi-Pass%20is%20a%20must.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https