n%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-hates-chatgpt-name-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20%26quot%3Ba%20horrible%20name%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20Trevor%20Noah's%20podcast%20in%202023%20and%20acknowledged%20as%20recently%20as%20July%20that%20the%20company%20needed%20to%20%26quot%3Brevamp%26quot%3B%20its%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20moment%20when%20OpenAI%20fans%20believed%20the%20new%20model%20might%20be%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-hints-at-project-strawberry-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BStrawberry%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20(for%20reasons%20only%20the%20most%20hardcore%20stans%20would%20understand).%20But%20in%20its%20press%20release%20announcing%20o1%2C%20the%20company%20explained%20how%20it%20ultimately%20settled%20on%20the%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20complex%20reasoning%20tasks%20this%20is%20a%20significant%20advancement%20and%20represents%20a%20new%20level%20of%20AI%20capability%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%20%26quot%3BGiven%20this%2C%20we%20are%20resetting%20the%20counter%20back%20to%201%20and%20naming%20this%20series%20OpenAI%20o1.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20OpenAI's%20latest%20branding%20mistake%2C%20according%20to%20o1.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdf336a8-04ba-40d0-985e-41762c4c3a7d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20asked%20o1%20to%20rate%20and%20give%20an%20'honest%20reaction'%20to%20its%20name.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%20presenting%20onstage%20with%20the%20OpenAI%20logo%20behind%20him.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a256d95a8a7bf049196e7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222801%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman.%3Cp%3EJason%20Redmond%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20o1%20to%20give%20its%20opinion%20on%20its%20name%20with%20the%20following%20prompt%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPretend%20you%20are%20a%20marketing%20or%20branding%20expert.%20What%20would%20be%20your%20honest%20reaction%20to%20an%20AI%20company%20pitching%20an%20AI%20LLM%20model%20name%20as%20'o1'%3F%20Give%20it%20a%20grade%20or%20rating%20on%20a%20scale%20of%201-10%20and%20explain%20the%20reason%20for%20your%20grading%20and%20scoring.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3Eo1%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bthought%20for%2012%20seconds%26quot%3B%20before%20sharing%20its%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20marketing%20and%20branding%20expert%2C%20my%20honest%20reaction%20to%20naming%20an%20AI%20language%20model%20%26quot%3Bo1%26quot%3B%20is%20that%20it%20poses%20several%20significant%20challenges.%20I%20would%20rate%20this%20name%20a%204%20out%20of%2010%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20said%20the%20name%20o1%20is%20too%20abstract%2C%20lacks%20brand%20identity%2C%20and%20could%20cause%20trademark%20concerns.%20o1%20also%20said%20its%20name%20could%20face%20SEO%20challenges%2C%20and%20customers%20could%20confuse%20the%20%26quot%3Bo%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20%26quot%3B0.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20might%20have%20human-like%20reasoning%20skills%2C%20it%20doesn't%20appear%20to%20have%20a%20human-like%20ability%20to%20deliver%20feedback%20gently%20or%20with%20tact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20name%20'o1'%20lacks%20the%20distinctiveness%20and%20communicative%20power%20needed%20for%20effective%20branding%20of%20an%20AI%20language%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20lead%20to%20confusion%2C%20be%20hard%20to%20find%20online%2C%20and%20doesn't%20help%20in%20building%20a%20strong%2C%20memorable%20brand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235d1d530-c7df-40e8-a85b-65a82fb1cf68%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20what%20should%20OpenAI%20have%20named%20o1%20instead%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20asked%20o1%20for%20alternative%20names.%20The%20model%20%26quot%3Bthought%26quot%3B%20for%20eight%20seconds%20and%20provided%2010%20new%20options%2C%20including%20LexiAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReasoning%3A%20Combines%20'Lexi'%20(from%20'lexicon%2C'%20meaning%20vocabulary%20or%20language)%20with%20'AI%2C'%20indicating%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20focus%20on%20language%2C%26quot%3B%20o1%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20also%20suggested%20Linguista%2C%20EchoMind%2C%20NexText%2C%20Dialogix%2C%20WordSmith%20AI%2C%20Verba%2C%20InnovaLingo%2C%20Cognitext%2C%20and%20LuminaryAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3Eo1%20explained%20its%20reasoning%20for%20suggesting%20those%20names%2C%20citing%20relevance%2C%20memorability%2C%20trademark%20availability%2C%20SEO%2C%20and%20pronunciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20BI%20asked%20o1%20a%20third%20question%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20if%20the%20main%20advancement%20in%20the%20model%20was%20that%20the%20AI%20model%20could%20follow%20a%20'chain%20of%20thought'%20and%20'reason'%20in%20a%20way%20previous%20models%20couldn't%3F%20What%20names%20would%20you%20suggest%20then%3F%26quot%3B%20BI%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3Eo1%20responded%20after%2015%20seconds%20of%20thought%20and%20provided%2020%20potential%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLogicFlow%2C%26quot%3B%20o1%20said.%20%26quot%3BReasoning%3A%20Conveys%20a%20continuous%20flow%20of%20logic%2C%20indicating%20advanced%20reasoning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20names%20on%20the%20list%20were%20CogniChain%2C%20LogicLink%2C%20SynapChain%2C%20MindFlow%2C%20CogniPath%2C%20and%20IntelliThread.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20the%20other%20two%20prompts%2C%20o1%20provided%20its%20reasoning%20for%20choosing%20those%20names%20and%20suggested%20actions%20we%20could%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20selecting%20a%20name%20that%20encapsulates%20the%20AI%20model's%20unique%20reasoning%20capabilities%2C%20you%20position%20your%20product%20as%20a%20pioneering%20solution%20in%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20o1%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-o1-product-name-strawberry-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726319104000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e44b2dcfb7f307e5716093%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-o1-product-name-strawberry-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20admitted%20OpenAI%20needs%20better%20product%20names%2C%20so%20BI%20asked%20its%20latest%20model%20for%20advice.%20o1%20rated%20its%20own%20name%20a%204%2F10.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-o1-product-name-strawberry-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'If%20India%20Don't%20Honour%20ICC%20Commitments...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-Pak%20Star's%20Massive%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20team's%20participation%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20-%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Pakistan%20-%20remains%20in%20doubt%20with%20the%20BCCI%20not%20making%20any%20official%20announcement.%20The%20two%20sides%20have%20not%20played%20a%20single%20bilateral%20series%20against%20each%20other%20in%20almost%20a%20decade%20and%20the%20only%20time%20they%20face%20off%20is%20during%20international%20and%20continental%20competitions.%20However%2C%20Pakistan%20did%20travel%20to%20India%20for%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20but%20India%20have%20not%20take%20any%20final%20decision.%20While%20there%20have%20been%20some%20reports%20of%20the%20tournament%20adapting%20a%20hybrid%20format%2C%20the%20ICC%20have%20no%20said%20anything%20on%20those%20lines%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20reportedly%20planned%20India's%20matches%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Lahore.%20Former%20Pakistan%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Moin%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F305-moin-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMoin%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20fired%20a%20warning%20for%20India%20and%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20Cricket%20Pakistan%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20BCCI%20should%20honour%20ICC%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20must%20honour%20ICC%20commitments%2C%20and%20if%20they%20don't%2C%20Pakistan%20should%20also%20consider%20taking%20a%20stand%20by%20not%20participating%20in%20future%20tournaments%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Moin%20Khan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20view%2C%20Indian%20cricket%20legends%20should%20advise%20the%20BCCI%20to%20keep%20sports%20separate%20from%20politics.%20Fans%20worldwide%20want%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20to%20play%2C%20benefiting%20not%20just%20Pakistan%20but%20the%20sport%20as%20a%20whole.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Moin%20also%20said%20his%20son%20Azam's%20confidence%20had%20taken%20a%20beating%20because%20of%20the%20way%20he%20was%20treated%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20held%20former%20PCB%20chairman%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ramiz%20Raja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41527-rameez-raja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERamiz%20Raja%3C%2Fa%3E%20responsible%20for%20the%20damage%20done%20to%20his%20son's%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoin%2C%20a%20former%20wicketkeeper-batter%20like%20his%20son%2C%20said%20that%20after%20watching%20all%20the%20matches%20Pakistan%20played%20during%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20Americas%2C%20he%20could%20confidently%20say%20that%20his%20son%20was%20best%20suited%20for%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20watched%20the%20entire%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20matches%20leading%20up%20to%20it%2C%20and%20it%20seemed%20like%20Azam%20was%20the%20number%20one%20choice%20for%20wicket-keeping%20and%20batting.%20Then%20suddenly%2C%20after%20just%20one%20match%2C%20the%20entire%20strategy%20was%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%C2%A0Moin%2C%20who%20scored%20more%20than%206%2C000%20international%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzam%20faced%20considerable%20ire%20from%20fans%20regarding%20his%20fitness%2C%20with%20his%20golden%20duck%20against%20the%20United%20States%20team%20not%20going%20down%20well%20with%20the%20cricket-crazy%20Pakistani%20supporters.%20He%20was%20dropped%20in%20the%20subsequent%20match%20against%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726318800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F4753f54_india-pakistan-afp_625x300_08_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fif-india-dont-honour-icc-commitments-ex-pakistan-stars-massive-warning-6564675%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20cricket%20team's%20participation%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20-%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Pakistan%20-%20remains%20in%20doubt%20with%20the%20BCCI%20not%20making%20any%20official%20announcement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fif-india-dont-honour-icc-commitments-ex-pakistan-stars-massive-warning-6564675%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Pseudo-Satellite%3A%20Solar%20Plane%20That%20Can%20Fly%20For%2090%20Days%20At%20A%20Time%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20will%20be%20a%20significant%20addition%20to%20India's%20arsenal%2C%20scientists%20have%20been%20developing%20a%20solar-powered%20plane%20that%20can%20fly%20up%20to%2090%20days%20at%20a%20stretch%2C%20and%20a%20smaller%20version%20has%20been%20flown%20successfully%20for%20ten%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalled%20a%20High-Altitude%20Platform%20(HAP)%2C%20it%20has%20been%20developed%20by%20the%20National%20Aerospace%20Laboratories%20(NAL)%2C%20Bengaluru.%20HAP%20is%20a%20solar-powered%20autonomous%20unmanned%20aircraft%20flying%20at%20stratospheric%20levels%20and%20is%20capable%20of%20day-and-night%20operations%20at%20altitudes%20of%2017-20%20km%20with%20an%20endurance%20of%20months.%20A%20HAP%20with%20a%20payload%20is%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20a%20High-Altitude%20Pseudo%20Satellite%20(HAPS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20startup%20in%20Bengaluru%20called%20New%20Space%20Research%20and%20Technologies%20has%20also%20developed%20a%20similar%20prototype%20with%2024-hour%20endurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NAL%2C%20during%20times%20of%20conflict%2C%20HAPS%20can%20address%20the%20perpetual%20theatre%20and%20strategic%20air%20asset%20shortfall%2C%20particularly%20during%20force%20mobilisation.%20It%20can%20fill%20both%20strategic%20and%20tactical%20roles%20of%20ISR%20(Intelligence%2C%20Surveillance%2C%20Reconnaissance)%20and%20can%20also%20provide%20battlefield%20communications.%20When%20used%20by%20air%20defence%20services%2C%20such%20aircraft%20can%20play%20an%20additional%20role%20in%20directing%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20suggest%20that%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20the%20only%20functional%20HAPS%20in%20the%20world%20is%20the%20Airbus%20Zephyr%2C%20which%20has%20demonstrated%20a%2064-day%20continuous%20flight%20in%20the%20Arizona%20desert%20in%20the%20US.%20Several%20efforts%20are%20on%C2%A0%20worldwide%20to%20develop%20such%20platforms%2C%20including%20in%20the%20US%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Germany%20and%20New%20Zealand.%20This%20makes%20it%20a%20very%20topical%20problem%20for%20testing%20the%20capabilities%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research-National%20Aerospace%20Laboratories%20(CSIR-NAL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSIR-NAL%20carried%20out%20a%20series%20of%20flight%20trials%20on%20the%20solar-secondary%20battery%20subscale%20High%20Altitude%20Platform%20vehicle%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20at%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation's%20aeronautical%20test%20range%20(ATR)%20at%20Challakere%2C%20Karnataka.%20The%20aircraft%20was%20equipped%20with%20all%20payloads%20and%20flight%20systems%2C%20though%20in%20a%20reduced%20size%2C%20as%20would%20be%20needed%20on%20the%20full-scale%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%2C%20which%20has%20a%20wingspan%20of%20nearly%2012%20metres%20(nearly%2040%20feet)%2C%20weighs%20less%20than%2022%20kg%20when%20fully%20equipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEye%20In%20The%20Sky%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20L%20Venkatakrishnan%2C%20Head%2C%20HAPS%20Program%2C%20National%20Aerospace%20Laboratories%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20potent%20solar-powered%20eye%20in%20the%20sky%2C%20much%20cheaper%20and%20more%20versatile%20than%20a%20satellite%2C%20easy%20to%20deploy%20and%20keep%20in%20the%20air%20for%20weeks%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Venkatakrishnan%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20aircraft%20met%20or%20exceeded%20all%20the%20performance%20metrics%20set%20out%20for%20it%20including%20a%20flight%20endurance%20of%20more%20than%208.5%20hours%2C%20reaching%20an%20altitude%20of%20almost%203%20km%20above%20mean%20sea%20level.%20With%20a%20high-performance%20solar%20PV%20(photovoltaic%20cell)%20and%20battery%20system%2C%20the%20subscale%20can%20reach%20a%2024-hour%20endurance%2C%20with%20a%20payload%20of%20about%201kg%2C%20making%20it%20useful%20for%20several%20low-altitude%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NAL%20requirement%20for%20a%20full-scale%20HAPS%20includes%20an%20assisted%20launch%20from%20the%20southern%20tip%20of%20India%2C%20with%20the%20aircraft%20climbing%20to%20above%20the%20sub-tropical%20jet%20stream%20(from%205%20km%20to%2015%20km)%2C%20which%20exists%20over%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20country%2C%20before%20reaching%20a%2020-degree%20latitude.%20Other%20requirements%20include%20a%20service%20ceiling%20of%2023%20km%20and%20a%20payload%20carrying%20capacity%20of%2015%20kg.%20The%20aircraft%20should%20also%20be%20able%20to%20take%20off%20from%20a%20field%20with%20a%20length%20of%20150-200%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20endurance%20will%20be%20dependent%20on%20factors%20including%20atmospheric%20conditions%20and%20equipment%20performance%2C%20NAL%20is%20aiming%20to%20achieve%2090%20days%20of%20HAPS%20operations.%20Dr%20Venkatakrishnan%20says%20the%20final%20version%20will%20have%20a%20wingspan%20which%20will%20be%20as%20wide%20as%20an%20Airbus%20320%2C%20but%20weigh%20only%20as%20much%20as%20a%20regular%20motorcycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20advantage%20of%20HAPS%20is%20that%20it%20can%20be%20used%20to%20continuously%20monitor%20enemy%20territory%20-%20day%20or%20night%20-%20once%20it%20is%20equipped%20with%20the%20right%20sensors%2C%20making%20it%20a%20unique%20bird%20in%20the%20sky%20that%20can%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20some%20of%20India's%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726318440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fe5mn2v8g_haps-solar-powered-plane-uav_625x300_14_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-pseudo-satellite-solar-plane-that-can-fly-for-90-days-at-a-time-6564634%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20what%20will%20be%20a%20significant%20addition%20to%20India's%20arsenal%2C%20scientists%20have%20been%20developing%20a%20solar-powered%20plane%20that%20can%20fly%20up%20to%2090%20days%20at%20a%20stretch%2C%20and%20a%20smaller%20version%20has%20been%20flown%20successfully%20for%20ten%20hours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-pseudo-satellite-solar-plane-that-can-fly-for-90-days-at-a-time-6564634%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Earth%20To%20Get%20A%20Mini-Moon%20For%202%20Months%3F%20All%20You%20Need%20To%20Know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEarth's%20moon%20will%20soon%20have%20a%20temporary%20junior%20companion%2C%20an%20apparent%20mini%20moon%20revolving%20around%20our%20planet%20for%20about%20two%20months.%20In%20a%20rare%20event%2C%20an%20asteroid%20will%20be%20captured%20by%20Earth's%20gravity%20and%20will%20orbit%20the%20earth%20from%20September%2029%20to%20November%2025%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20asteroid%202024%20PT5%20was%20spotted%20on%20August%207%20using%20the%20Asteroid%20Terrestrial-Impact%20Last%20Alert%20System%20(ATLAS)%2C%20a%20NASA-funded%20asteroid%20impact%20early%20warning%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiopscience.iop.org%2Farticle%2F10.3847%2F2515-5172%2Fad781f%5C%22%3EResearch%20Notes%20of%20the%20American%20Astronomical%20Society%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20asteroid%20is%20not%20too%20big%20with%20a%20diameter%20of%20just%2010%20metre%20(33%20feet).%20During%20its%2053-day%20tenure%20around%20the%20earth%2C%202024%20PT5%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20make%20a%20full%20orbit%2C%20instead%20it%20will%20perform%20a%20horseshoe%20loop%20before%20breaking%20away%20from%20the%20earth's%20gravitational%20pull.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RNAAS%20report%2C%20authored%20by%20Carlos%20de%20la%20Fuente%20Marcos%20and%20Raul%20de%20la%20Fuente%20Marcos%2C%20says%20that%20Earth%20has%20a%20tendency%20to%20capture%20asteroids%20and%20pull%20them%20into%20its%20orbit.%20These%20asteroids%20sometimes%20perform%20one%20or%20more%20full%20revolutions%20around%20our%20planet%20while%20other%20times%2C%20they%20break%20away%20from%20the%20earth's%20elliptical%20path%20before%20completing%20an%20orbit.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20an%20asteroid%20captured%20by%20Earth's%20gravity%20revolved%20around%20it%20for%20a%20year%20from%20July%202006%20to%20July%202007.%20However%2C%20the%20newly%20discovered%202024%20PT5%20seems%20to%20resemble%20the%20path%20of%202022%20NX1%2C%20a%20temporary%20flyby%20that%20revolved%20around%20Earth%20in%201981%20and%202022%20without%20ever%20completing%20an%20orbit%20and%20will%20likely%20return%20to%20take%20another%20semi%20round%20in%202051.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Earth%20may%20sometimes%20pull%20space%20junk%20into%20its%20orbit%2C%20the%20report%20says%20that%202024%20PT5%20is%20a%20natural%20object%20as%20%26quot%3Bits%20short-term%20dynamical%20evolution%20closely%20resembles%20that%20of%202022%20NX1%2C%20a%20confirmed%20natural%20object.%26quot%3B%20The%20report%20also%20indicates%20that%20its%20orbital%20properties%20resemble%20that%20of%20asteroids%20that%20come%20from%20the%20Arjuna%20asteroid%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726318320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fnaoo5i6_earth-generic_625x300_08_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fearth-to-get-a-mini-moon-for-2-months-all-you-need-to-know-6565044%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Earth's%20moon%20will%20soon%20have%20a%20temporary%20junior%20companion%2C%20an%20apparent%20mini%20moon%20revolving%20around%20our%20planet%20for%20about%20two%20months.%20In%20a%20rare%20event%2C%20an%20asteroid%20will%20be%20captured%20by%20Earth's%20gravity%20and%20will%20orbit%20the%20earth%20from%20Sept%2029%20to%20Nov%2025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fearth-to-get-a-mini-moon-for-2-months-all-you-need-to-know-6565044%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20defends%20'loony'%20Laura%20Loomer%20amid%20MAGA%20meltdown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726317927000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113351295%2Cimgsize-1874789.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-defends-loony-laura-loomer-amid-maga-meltdown%2Farticleshow%2F113351267.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20is%20under%20fire%20from%20Republican%20allies%20over%20his%20association%20with%20far-right%20activist%20Laura%20Loomer.%20Despite%20her