%26quot%3BVoldemort%26quot%3B%20in%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20appearance%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNoFchfFa0i8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BHappy%20Sad%20Confused%20podcast%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Josh%20Horowitz%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20said%20that%20at%20the%20start%20of%20his%20career%2C%20he%20auditioned%20for%20the%20role%20of%20Tom%20Riddle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20nearly%20in%20'Harry%20Potter.'%20Almost%2C%26quot%3B%20McAvoy%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20very%20first%20movie%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was.%20Tom%20Riddle%20is%20in%20the%20first%20one%2C%20right%3F%20But%20he's%20like%20in%20it%20for%20like%20a%20scene%2C%20in%20a%20flashback%20or%20something%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20crazy%2C%20I'd%20hardly%20done%20any%20work.%20And%20me%20and%20I%20think%20maybe%2010%20other%20actors%20or%20something%20like%20that%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20put%20us%20on%20a%20retainer%20so%20they%20could%20hold%20us%20and%20keep%20us%20to%20choose%20later.%20It%20was%20a%20really%20strange%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcAvoy%20said%20that%20they%20offered%20him%20%26quot%3Ba%20ton%20of%20money%26quot%3B%20to%20accept%20the%20job.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%20%C2%A340%2C000%20(%2452%2C000)%20or%20something%20like%20that%2C%20and%20I'd%20done%20very%20little%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20a%20catch%2C%20he%20said.%20If%20he%20had%20agreed%20to%20the%20retainer%2C%20he%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20able%20to%20do%20any%20work%20for%20around%20seven%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20advice%20of%20his%20agent%2C%20whom%20he%20still%20has%20now%2C%20the%20actor%20declined%20the%20offer%2C%20and%20he%20went%20on%20to%20take%20a%20lower-paid%20theater%20role%20instead%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20making%26quot%3B%20of%20him%20as%20an%20a