%20pretty%2C%20I%20mean%20pretty%2C%20pretty%2C%20pretty%20classic%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20think%20that%20too%20many%20people%20are%20bullish%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20sounds%20counterintuitive%2C%20Belski%20is%20worried%20about%20the%20stock%20market%20moving%20significantly%20higher%2C%20not%20lower%2C%20from%20here%2C%20because%20that%20would%20set%20up%20a%20prime%20environment%20for%20a%20sharp%20pullback%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20see%20a%20super%20spike%20now.%20I%20think%20the%20faster%20the%20market%20goes%20up%20right%20now%2C%20that%20would%20worry%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20many%20investors%20feeling%20bullish%20about%20stocks%2C%20the%20market%20is%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20a%20sell-off%20if%20there's%20a%20macro%20surprise%20that%20badly%20misses%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20sentiment%20perspective%2C%20we're%20one%20bad%20macro%20data%20point%20away%20from%20a%20pullback%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20what%20that%20macro%20data%20point%20could%20be%2C%20a%20surprise%20surge%20in%20inflation%2C%20a%20really%20bad%20jobs%20report%2C%20or%20a%20big%20miss%20from%20Nvidia%20all%20come%20to%20mind%20for%20Belski.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22664aaf94-29d7-4cd0-8675-f7ebca4f3a49%5C%22%3EYardeni%20Research's%20Eric%20Wallerstein%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Wallerstein%2C%20chief%20market%20strategist%20at%20Yardeni%20Research%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20there%20are%20two%20tail%20risks%20that%20could%20halt%20the%20stock%20market's%20advance%20that%20should%20be%20on%20investors'%20radars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20one%20is%20rising%20geopolitical%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20the%20Middle%20East%20blows%20out%2C%20Russia-Ukraine%2C%20China-Taiwan%2C%20like%20just%20the%20overall%20geopolitical%20scene%20is%20much%20more%20tense%2C%26quot%3B%20Wallerstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20populist%20movements%20and%20nationalism%20are%20gaining%20popularity%20in%20countries%20around%20the%20world%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20great%20for%20a%20globalized%20economy%2C%20according%20to%20Wallerstein.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20just%20leads%20to%20a%20world%20with%20less%20strand%20and%20less%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Wallerstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20risk%20is%2C%20similar%20to%20Belski's%20concern%2C%20a%201990's%20type%20melt-up%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20is%2C%20valuations%20expand%20and%20you%20kind%20of%20get%20a%20blow%20off%20top%2C%20because%20the%20market%20gets%20too%20ebullient%2C%20and%20then%20that%20creates%20the%20conditions%20to%20get%20a%20bear%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Wallerstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20Fed%20could%20pour%20gasoline%20onto%20the%20fire%20if%20it%20cuts%20interest%20rates%20aggressively%2C%20according%20to%20Wallerstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20do%20cut%20that%20much%2C%20which%20is%20such%20an%20extreme%20path%20of%20policy%2C%20I%20think%20that%20blow%20off%20top%20becomes%20increasingly%20likely%2C%20and%20it's%20definitely%20something%20we're%20worried%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Wallerstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20riding%20a%20bubble%20on%20the%20way%20up%20isn't%20a%20bad%20thing%2C%20it's%20the%20sharp%20and%20quick%20downturn%20that%20often%20follows%20a%20bubble%20peak%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20period%20of%20significant%20underperformance%20for%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ae1cfb1-3240-4f20-86f9-151f36be49a8%5C%22%3ECarson%20Group's%20Sonu%20Varghese%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESonu%20Varghese%2C%20global%20macro%20strategist%20at%20Carson%20Group%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bthinking%20about%20rising%20risks%20for%20a%20few%20months%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20still%20like%20equities%20and%20haven't%20changed%20our%20overweight%2C%20but%20we've%20increased%20our%20exposure%20to%20diversifiers%20like%20long-term%20treasuries%20and%20low%20volatility%20equities%2C%26quot%3B%20Varghese%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVarghese's%20more%20defensive%20portfolio%20posture%20is%20driven%20mostly%20by%20what%20a%20policy%20mistake%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20could%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20inflation%20fight%20largely%20over%2C%20and%20labor%20market%20trends%20broadly%20weakening%2C%20%26quot%3Bpolicy%20is%20too%20tight%2C%26quot%3B%20Varghese%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20risk%20is%20that%20the%20Fed%20doesn't%20act%20aggressively%20enough%20to%20arrest%20the%20labor%20market%20downtrend%2C%20and%20instead%20follows%20a%20gradual%20approach%20to%20rate%20cuts%20that%20leaves%20them%20further%20behind%20the%20curve.%20Which%20also%20means%20they'll%20have%20to%20do%20larger%20catch%20up%20cuts%20later%20on%20(a%20re-run%20of%20what%20happened%20in%202022%2C%20but%20from%20the%20opposite%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Varghese%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20sees%20no%20risk%20of%20an%20imminent%20recession%2C%20he%20said%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20recession%20will%20rise%20within%20the%20next%20six%20to%2012%20months%20if%20the%20Fed%20falls%20far%20behind%20the%20curve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20could%20potentially%20impact%20equities%20-%20bad%20economic%20data%20will%20likely%20be%20traded%20as%20bad%20news%20by%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20Varghese%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20all%20three%20of%20these%20strategists%20are%20sticking%20with%20stocks%20and%20still%20have%20a%20bullish%20view%20of%20what%20lies%20ahead%20for%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20they%20worry%20about%20the%20neverending%20list%20of%20potential%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com