ef%20Financial%20Officer%20Brian%20West%20warned%20a%20prolonged%20walkout%20could%20hurt%20output%20and%20%26quot%3Bjeopardize%20our%20recovery%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoeing%20is%20a%20systemically%20important%20company%20for%20global%20aviation%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20O'Connor%2C%20chief%20financial%20officer%20of%20Irish%20leasing%20company%20Avolon%2C%20told%20Reuters%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20strike%20%26quot%3Bcould%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20production%20levels%2C%20which%20could%20exacerbate%20some%20of%20the%20supply%20shortages%20that%20are%20in%20the%20market%20at%20the%20moment%20for%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20after%20Avolon%20announced%20it%20had%20acquired%20a%20large%20portfolio%20of%20jets%20from%20Castlelake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAirlines%20have%20struggled%20to%20expand%20capacity%20to%20meet%20rising%20demand%20as%20supplies%20of%20jetliners%20are%20curtailed%20by%20parts%20shortages%2C%20industry-wide%20recruitment%20problems%20and%20overloaded%20maintenance%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20have%20been%20warning%20the%20most%20promising%20part%20of%20the%20industry's%20all-important%20business%20cycle%20could%20run%20out%20before%20airlines%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20enjoy%20the%20full%20benefits%20of%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20time%20before%20we%20see%20that%20balance.%20I'm%20starting%20to%20evolve%20the%20hypothesis%20that%20it%20won't%20be%20(extra)%20supply%20that%20corrects%20it%2C%20but%20instead%20a%20softening%20of%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rob%20Morris%2C%20global%20head%20of%20consultancy%20at%20Cirium%20Ascend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20say%20high%20air%20fares%20-%20although%20good%20for%20airlines%20in%20the%20short%20term%20-%20could%20themselves%20accelerate%20that%20tipping%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20view%20is%20that%20(average%20fares)%20will%20rise%3B%20and%20when%20ticket%20prices%20go%20up%2C%20then%20all%20other%20things%20being%20equal%2C%20you%20have%20lower%20traffic%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20aviation%20economist%20Adam%20Pilarski%2C%20senior%20vice-president%20at%20AVITAS%20consultancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Boeing%20halts%20production%20of%20its%20most-sold%20jet%2C%20European%20rival%20Airbus%20is%20also%20struggling%20to%20meet%20its%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAirbus%20Chief%20Executive%20Guillaume%20Faury%20expressed%20optimism%20at%20a%20U.S.%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20conference%20this%20week%20that%20the%20European%20planemaker%20would%20meet%20a%20recently%20lowered%20target%20of%20770%20deliveries%20this%20year%2C%20following%20a%20profit%20warning%20and%20engine%20supply%20glitch%20in%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20following%20a%20short-lived%20spike%20in%20deliveries%20in%20July%2C%20industry%20sources%20questioned%20how%20comfortably%20the%20world's%20largest%20planemaker%20would%20exceed%20last%20year's%20735.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDwindling%20numbers%20of%20planes%20in%20storage%20and%20record-high%20utilization%20of%20existing%20planes%20confirm%20the%20supply%20squeeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFLEET%20AGE%20RISING%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Boeing's%20lower%20production%20levels%20compared%20to%20Airbus%20may%20limit%20the%20incremental%20effect%20of%20the%20strike.%20Yet%20analysts%20said%20airlines%20have%20little%20room%20to%20maneuver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20leasing%20companies%20also%20running%20out%20of%20available%20capacity%2C%20carriers%20need%20to%20keep%20existing%20jets%20flying%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20the%20average%20age%20of%20the%20fleet%20declined%20as%20airlines%20and%20leasing%20companies%20took%20advantage%20of%20low%20interest%20rates%20to%20invest%20in%20new%20fuel-saving%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20the%20average%20age%20of%20the%20widely%20flown%20single-aisle%20jet%20fleet%20was%20about%2010.2%20years%2C%20according%20to%20Cirium%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20dipping%20to%209.1%20years%20during%20the%20pandemic%20as%20airlines%20grounded%20fleets%2C%20the%20age%20started%20growing%20again.%20It%20now%20stands%20at%2011.3%20years%20%26quot%3Band%20still%20heading%20upwards%2C%26quot%3B%20Morris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20despite%20efforts%20to%20reach%20net%20zero%20emissions%20by%202050%2C%20which%20rely%20partly%20on%20modernizing%20the%20planes%20in%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20must%20mean%20that%20we're%20burning%20more%20CO2%20than%20we%20should%20be%20because%20we're%20using%20more%20old%20aircraft...so%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20can%20go%20wrong%20is%20sustainability%2C%26quot%3B%20Morris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20industry%20says%20it%20is%20confident%20of%20reaching%20a%20target%20of%20net%20zero%20emissions%20by%202050.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726316160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fe6oab0j_boeing-plane-manufacturing-plant-boeing-manufacturing-reuters_625x300_14_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-boeing-strike-could-make-the-global-jetliner-shortage-worse-6564811%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Boeing's%20first%20strike%20in%2016%20years%20could%20further%20compound%20global%20shortages%20of%20jetliners%20that%20have%20been%20pushing%20up%20airfares%20and%20forcing%20airlines%20to%20keep%20older%20jets%20flying%20longer%2C%20industry%20executives%20and%20analysts%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-boeing-strike-could-make-the-global-jetliner-shortage-worse-6564811%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22am