Fhomeowners-insurance%2Fflorida%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520average%2520home%2520insurance%2520cost%2520for%2520Florida%2Cinclude%2520Travelers%252C%2520Nationwide%252C%2520and%2520Security%2520First%2520Insurance.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsurify%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20insane.%20It's%20craziness%20how%20much%20more%20we're%20paying%20for%20homeowners'%20insurance%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20pretty%20common%20across%20the%20whole%20state%20right%20now.%20Everyone%20is%20having%20issues%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20living%20has%20also%20risen%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20rising%20housing%20costs%20and%20more%20people%20living%20in%20the%20city.%20Consumer%20prices%20in%20the%20Miami%2C%20Fort%20Lauderdale%2C%20and%20West%20Palm%20Beach%20areas%20of%20Florida%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FCUURA320SA0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eup%20around%2030%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20February%202020%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics.%20Prices%20in%20Tampa%2C%20St.%20Petersburg%2C%20and%20Clearwater%20areas%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FCUUSA321SA0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eup%2025%25%20since%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20prices%20have%20accounted%20for%20a%20big%20portion%20of%20that%20increase.%20The%20median%20home%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redfin.com%2Fstate%2FFlorida%2Fhousing-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlorida%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20costs%20%24409%2C700%2C%20up%20by%20about%2055%25%20from%20the%20median%20house%20price%20recorded%20in%20February%202023%2C%20Redfin%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20one%20of%20the%20main%20draws%20of%20Florida%20has%20always%20been%20that%20it's%20cheaper%2C%26quot%3B%20Darryl%20Fairweather%2C%20the%20chief%20economist%20of%20Redfin%2C%20said%2C