rce%2C%20Fairweather%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20it%20still%20attract%20people%3F%20I%20think%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20McBride%20said.%20%26quot%3B%5BBut%5D%20I%20wouldn't%20live%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-housing-market-sales-weather-climate-change-retirement-pandemic-costs-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726315862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e1c5c0a0ff598b26668d08%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-housing-market-sales-weather-climate-change-retirement-pandemic-costs-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Soaring%20home%20insurance%20costs%20amid%20extreme%20weather%20are%20among%20the%20factors%20making%20Florida%20less%20appealing%20to%20current%20residents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-housing-market-sales-weather-climate-change-retirement-pandemic-costs-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22David%20Zaslav%20risked%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery's%20future%20by%20passing%20on%20the%20NBA%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20the%20gamble%20might%20pay%20off%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225694%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20Zaslav%2C%20CEO%20of%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%2C%20arrives%20at%20the%20Sun%20Valley%20Lodge%20for%20the%20Allen%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20Sun%20Valley%20Conference%20on%20July%2011%2C%202023%20in%20Sun%20Valley%2C%20Idaho%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661423af1caec1275a6dd01c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223796%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Discovery%20CEO%20David%20Zaslav%20shocked%20Wall%20Street%20and%20is%20hoping%20to%20do%20so%20ag