d%20to%20pay%20the%20same%20rates%20for%20an%20NBA-less%20TNT%20in%20its%20next%20deal%20and%20%3Cem%3Ehigher%3C%2Fem%3E%20rates%20for%20WBD's%20other%20networks%2C%20like%20HGTV%20and%20Food%20Network%2C%20Business%20Insider%20confirmed.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwbd-hbo-max-charter-deal-tnt-nba-cable-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20catch%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20WBD%20will%20now%20give%20Max%20%E2%80%94%20including%20its%20coveted%20HBO%20content%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0for%20free%20to%20all%20Charter%20customers%20who%20want%20it%20(though%20that%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwbd-earnings-report-nba-tv-media-deal-nbc-tnt-zaslav-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboost%20the%20streamer's%20advertising%20business)%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWBD%20likely%20hopes%20that%20the%20deal%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20precedent%20in%20its%20upcoming%20carriage%20negotiations%20with%20other%20pay-TV%20providers%2C%20including%20important%20players%20like%20Comcast%20and%20DirecTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWBD%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213930ffd-4d34-48f2-9ecc-dbdd6cd2ce33%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Charter%20deal%20is%20a%20coup%20for%20WBD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20has%20had%20little%20confidence%20in%20Zaslav%20and%20company%20lately.%20WBD%20shares%20had%20been%20down%2040%25%20in%202024%20alone%2C%20and%20some%20believed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarner-bros-discovery-wbd-zaslav-struggles-streaming-media-strategy-analysis-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreaking%20up%20the%20conglomerate%20was%20the%20best%20option%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20a%20few%20media%20analysts%20say%20that%20if%20WBD%20could%20receive%20the%20same%20rates%20for%20its%20networks%20without%20the%20NBA%2C%20the%20company's%20fortunes%20will%20be%20looking%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20WBD%20get%20affiliation%20deals%20done%20without%20dramatic%20reductions%20in%20affiliate%20fees%3F%20If%20they%20can%20execute%2C%20investor%20fears%20are%20misplaced%20and%20the%20stock%20decline%20is%20overdone%2C%26quot%3B%20Rich%20Greenfield%20of%20LightShed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flightshedtmt.com%2F2024%2F08%2F08%2Fwhat-did-wbd-say-or-not-say-last-night-that-spooked-investors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20an%20August%208%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20WBD's%20Q2%20earnings%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20news%20that%20WBD%20had%20done%20just%20that%20with%20Charter%2C%20Greenfield%20heaped%20praise%20on%20WBD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20clear%20winner%20is%20David%20Zaslav%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%2C%26quot%3B%20Greenfield%20wrote%20in%20a%20September%2012%20note.%20%26quot%3BWBD%20investors%20have%20grown%20increasingly%20concerned%20that%20Turner's%20loss%20of%20the%20NBA%20(still%20being%20litigated%2C%20but%20we%20doubt%20they%20win)%2C%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20dramatic%20reduction%20in%20affiliate%20fees%20to%20TNT%20and%20Turner%20more%20broadly%2C%20or%20even%20a%20loss%20of%20carriage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECraig%20Moffett%20of%20MoffettNathanson%20also%20loved%20the%20deal%2C%20telling%20BI%20in%20an%20email%20that%20both%20WBD%20and%20Charter%20got%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20expected%20an%20uphill%20battle%20for%20TNT%2C%20if%20not%20the%20entire%20Turner%20portfolio%2C%20to%20maintain%20rates%20in%20the%20face%20of%20losing%20NBA%20rights%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Moffett%20wrote%20in%20a%20September%2012%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoffett%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BNow%20that%20the%20Charter%20deal%20is%20in%20place%2C%20we%20think%20it%20helps%20remove%20one%20of%20the%20bigger%20risks%20to%20WBD%2C%20i.e.%20that%20the%20linear%20cable%20network%20cash%20flows%20decline%20will%20take%20another%20significant%20step%20down%20post-2025%20because%20of%20a%20change%20in%20trajectory%20in%20the%20rate%20of%20decline%20of%20affiliate%20fees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1678c6c-3823-4359-b244-4aae763ae08f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EComcast%20is%20prepared%20for%20combat%2C%20but%20Zaslav%20could%20get%20another%20win%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20pay-TV%20provider%20is%20going%20to%20take%20it%20easy%20in%20the%20next%20round%20of%20negotiations%20with%20WBD%2C%20but%20some%20industry%20experts%20think%20Comcast%20could%20be%20especially%20tough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharter%20and%20Comcast%20are%20both%20broadband%20providers%20with%20TV%20businesses%2C%20but%20the%20similarities%20stop%20there%20as%20far%20as%20negotiations%20with%20WBD%20are%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComcast%20%E2%80%94%20which%20owns%20NBCU%20%E2%80%94%20outbid%20WBD%20in%20the%20NBA%20deal%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnba-tv-deal-media-rights-deal-nbc-peacock-analyst-prediction-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboost%20its%20broadcast%20networks%20and%20streaming%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20also%20likely%20in%20part%20because%20it%20believes%20it%20can%20pay%20less%20for%20WBD's%20cable%20networks%20in%20its%20next%20deal.%20With%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20there's%20little%20doubt%20that%20Comcast%20CEO%20Brian%20Roberts%20will%20play%20hardball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPart%20of%20the%20reason%20Roberts's%20NBC%20Universal%20stole%20the%20NBA%20from%20Zaslav%20in%20the%20first%20place%20was%20to%20stick%20it%20to%20him%20in%20the%20next%20distribution%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20entertainment%20journalist%20Matt%20Belloni%20of%20Puck%20News%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpuck.news%2Fnewsletter_content%2Fwhat-im-hearing-a-new-tv-model-danas-debate-night-3%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20Thursday%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20that%20strategy%20has%20changed%2C%20and%20if%20Comcast%20scores%20reduced%20fees%2C%20Charter%20will%20start%20waving%20i