3A%20Spoilers%20ahead%20for%20Netflix's%20adaptation%20of%20Elin%20Hilderbrand's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Perfect%20Couple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EElin%20Hilderbrand's%20book%20and%20the%20Netflix%20series%20have%20some%20key%20differences%2C%20including%20the%20ending.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20novel%2C%20Merritt's%20death%20is%20an%20accident.%20In%20the%20series%2C%20it's%20a%20calculated%20crime.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-perfect-couple-opening-credits-dance-cast-explain-how-happened-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Perfect%20Couple%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Netflix's%20hit%20new%20murder-mystery%20series%2C%20follows%20Amelia%20Sacks%20(Eve%20Hewson)%20and%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20Benji%20Winbury%20(Billy%20Howle)%20ahead%20of%20their%20plush%20Nantucket%20wedding%2C%20which%20is%20called%20off%20after%20the%20dead%20body%20of%20the%20maid%20of%20honor%2C%20Merritt%20Monaco%20(Meghann%20Fahy)%2C%20is%20found%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20big%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenji's%20wealthy%20family%20immediately%20becomes%20fodder%20for%20tabloids%20and%20nosey%20neighbors%20as%20the%20police%20investigate%20every%20member%20of%20the%20wedding%20party%2C%20including%20Benji's%20famous%20crime%20writer%20mother%2C%20Greer%20Garrison%20Winbury%20(Nicole%20Kidman)%2C%20and%20his%20father%2C%20Tag%20Winbury%20(Liev%20Schreiber).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20is%20based%20on%20Elin%20Hilderbrand's%202018%20novel%20of%20the%20same%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20adaptation%20has%20kept%20the%20story%20largely%20the%20same%2C%20it%20may%20still%20surprise%20book%20readers%2C%20as%20showrunner%20Jenna%20Lamia%20and%20director%20Susanne%20Bier%20have%20tweaked%20a%20number%20of%20key%20details%2C%20including%20the%20story's%20ending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20ways%20the%20show%20differs%20from%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2270b92a34-2031