%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffarhan-akhtar-shares-behind-the-scenes-picture-of-120-bahadur-shoot-in-ladakh%2Farticleshow%2F113348171.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20How%20New%20'Mountain%20Tank'%20Will%20Enhance%20Army's%20Combat%20Capabilities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELearning%20lessons%20from%20the%20standoff%20with%20China%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20and%20fine-tuning%20them%20by%20observing%20what's%20been%20happening%20in%20the%20war%20between%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20has%20developed%20India's%20first%20'mountain%20tank'%2C%20Zorawar%2C%20which%20successfully%20completed%20its%20first%20phase%20of%20trials%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air-transportable%2C%2025-tonne%20combat%20platform%2C%20developed%20for%20high-altitude%20deployment%2C%20has%20been%20designed%20to%20meet%20India's%20needs%20on%20the%20frontier%20with%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20DRDO%20on%20September%2013%20successfully%20conducted%20the%20preliminary%20automotive%20trials%20of%20the%20Indian%20light%20Tank%2C%20Zorawar%2C%20a%20highly%20versatile%20platform%20capable%20of%20deployment%20in%20high-altitude%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20field%20trials%20conducted%20in%20the%20desert%20terrain%2C%20the%20light%20tank%20demonstrated%20exceptional%20performance%2C%20efficiently%20meeting%20all%20the%20intended%20objectives%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20described%20the%20successful%20trials%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20milestone%26quot%3B%20on%20%C2%A0India's%20path%20to%20self-reliance%20in%20critical%20defence%20systems%20and%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20by%20DRDO's%20Combat%20Vehicles%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Development%20Establishment%20(CVRDE)%20in%20association%20with%20Larsen%20and%20Toubro%2C%20the%20Army%20is%20planning%20to%20deploy%20350%20Zorawar%20tanks%2C%20mostly%20in%20mountainous%20terrain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDRDO%20had%20earlier%20developed%20the%20Arjun%2C%20a%20third-generation%20main%20battle%20tank%20weighing%2058.5%20tonnes%20but%2C%20after%20the%20confrontation%20with%20China%2C%20the%20need%20was%20felt%20for%20a%20lighter%20tank%20for%20hilly%20terrain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Makes%20It%20Special%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20in%20a%20record%20time%20of%20about%20three%20years%2C%20Zorawar%2C%20which%20means%20%26quot%3Bcourageous%26quot%3B%20in%20Punjabi%2C%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20be%20inducted%20into%20the%20Army%20in%20another%20three.%C2%A0The%20project%20has%20been%20named%20after%20General%20Zorawar%20Singh%20Kahluria%2C%20who%20had%20served%20under%20Raja%20Gulab%20Singh%20of%20Jammu's%20Dogra%20dynasty%20and%C2%A0%20helped%20expand%20the%20Dogra%20territory%20by%20conquering%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20light%2C%20it%20can%20be%20easily%20deployed%20in%20border%20areas%20by%20helicopter.%20Experts%20said%20the%20tank%20will%20prove%20to%20be%20very%20effective%20even%20in%20bad%20weather%20and%20difficult%20conditions%20on%20the%20northern%20border%2C%20and%20can%20also%20perform%20well%20in%20desert%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEquipped%20with%20armour%20which%20is%20strong%20for%20its%20category%20of%20tanks%2C%20it%20can%20wade%20through%20water%20as%20well.%20Its%20speed%20is%20about%2060%20kilometres%20per%20hour%20on%20land%20and%20it%20is%20equipped%20with%20the%20Cockerill%203105%20turret%20with%20a%20105-millimetre%20calibre%20gun.%20Machine%20guns%20can%20be%20mounted%20on%20it%20and%20anti-tank%20guided%20missiles%20can%20also%20be%20installed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20ability%20to%20fire%20at%20high%20angles%20of%20elevation%2C%20the%20tank%20can%20perform%20the%20role%20of%20limited%20artillery%20and%20it%20is%20a%20versatile%20platform%20which%20has%20been%20built%20in%20a%20modular%20fashion%20to%20accommodate%20future%20upgrades.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726309620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fm7ljt4j_zorawar_625x300_14_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-new-mountain-tank-will-enhance-armys-combat-capabilities-6564151%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Learning%20lessons%20from%20the%20standoff%20with%20China%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20and%20fine-tuning%20them%20by%20observing%20what's%20been%20happening%20in%20the%20war%20between%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20DRDO%20has%20developed%20India's%20first%20%26quot%3Bmountain%20tank%26quot%3B%2C%20Zorawar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-new-mountain-tank-will-enhance-armys-combat-capabilities-6564151%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Climate%20march%20shuts%20down%20Hague%20motorway%20during%20police%20strike%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726309551000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113348266%2Cimgsize-1523900.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fclimate-march-shuts-down-hague-motorway-during-police-strike%2Farticleshow%2F113348168.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113348168.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EExtinction%20Rebellion%20climate%20activists%20blocked%20a%20major%20motorway%20running%20through%20The%20Hague%20on%20Saturday%2C%20their%20%26quot%3Bmost%20disruptive%26quot%3B%20action%20yet%20to%20protest%20against%20billions%20of%20euros%20in%20