how%2F113347945.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-India%20Star%20Removed%20As%20Head%20Coach%20For%20Former%20WC%20Semi-Finalists%20Abruptly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20and%20Karnataka%20pacer%20Dodda%20Ganesh%20has%20been%20relieved%20of%20his%20duties%20as%20Kenya%20men's%20head%20coach%20just%20a%20month%20after%20his%20appointment%20into%20the%20role%20last%20month%20(August%2012).%20Ganesh%2C%20who%20played%20four%20Tests%20and%20one%20ODI%20for%20India%2C%20had%20been%20roped%20in%20for%20a%20year-long%20contract%20with%20the%20Kenya%20men's%20team.%20As%20per%20a%20report%20in%20nation.africa%2C%20the%20executive%20board%20of%20Cricket%20Kenya%20said%20Ganesh's%20appointment%20was%20made%20irregularly.%20The%20letter%20was%20signed%20by%20Pearlyne%20Omami%2C%20Cricket%20Kenya's%20Director%20of%20Women's%20Cricket%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20other%20board%20members.%20Kenya%20had%20entered%20the%202003%20World%20Cup%20semi-fnals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20a%20resolution%20of%20the%20executive%20board%20of%20Cricket%20Kenya%20passed%20on%20Wednesday%2C%2028%20August%202024%2C%20and%20anchored%20under%20inter%20alia%20Articles%205.9%20and%208.4.3%20of%20the%20Cricket%20Kenya%20Constitution%2C%20we%20wish%20to%20notify%20you%20that%20the%20executive%20board%20has%20declined%20to%20ratify%20your%20appointment%20as%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20men's%20cricket%20national%20team%20for%20want%20of%20following%20established%20procedures%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20aforementioned%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVoided%20the%20purported%20contract%20made%20on%20August%207%2C%202024%20between%20Mr%20Manoj%20Patel%20and%20yourself.%20Pursuant%20to%20the%20above%2C%20Cricket%20Kenya%20is%20not%20and%20shall%20not%20be%20bound%20by%20the%20said%20purported%20contract.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20therefore%20directed%20to%20cease%20any%20further%20engagement%20or%20dealings%20with%20the%20men's%20national%20cricket%20team%20with%20immediate%20effect.%20Any%20concerns%20or%20claims%20relating%20to%20this%20notice%20should%20be%20channeled%20to%20Mr%20Manoj%20Patel%20and%20any%20other%20individuals%20who%20irregularly%20and%20unprocedurally%20engaged%20you%20in%20this%20respect%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Ganesh's%20stint%20coming%20to%20an%20abrupt%20end%2C%20former%20international%20players%20Lameck%20Onyango%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Joseph%20Angara%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F104-joseph-angara-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJoseph%20Angara%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20take%20over%20as%20Kenya%20men's%20head%20coach%20and%20assistant%20coach%20respectively.%20The%20duo's%20first%20assignment%20will%20be%20to%20prepare%20the%20Kenyan%20team%20for%20the%20ICC%20Division%202%20Challenge%20League%2C%20where%20they%20will%20face%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%2C%20Qatar%2C%20Denmark%20and%20Jersey%2C%20in%20Nairobi%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20the%202026%20ICC%20Men's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20Africa%20Sub-regional%20Qualifier%20B%20tournament%2C%20where%20Kenya%20will%20play%20against%20Zimbabwe%2C%20Rwanda%2C%20Mozambique%2C%20Seychelles%2C%20and%20Gambia%20in%20Nairobi%20from%20October%2017-26.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726308420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fhs33i5mg_dodda-ganesh-rahul-dravid_625x300_14_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fex-india-star-dodda-ganesh-removed-as-head-coach-of-former-world-cup-semi-finalists-one-month-after-appointment-6564043%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20India%20star%20had%20played%20four%20tests%20and%20one%20ODI%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ACT%3A%20Harman's%20brace%20gives%20India