ient%2C%20as%20a%20problem%20in%20one%20small%20system%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20affect%20the%20entire%20area%E2%80%99s%20sanitation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Chorol%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20steps%20are%20critical%20given%20how%20groundwater%20is%20primarily%20used%20by%20households%2C%20industries%2C%20hotels%2C%20and%20various%20institutions%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Leh%20town%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.mongabay.com%2F2024%2F07%2Frapid-urbanisation-and-climate-change-threaten-groundwater-resources-in-ladakh-says-study%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMongabay%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Farooq%20Dar%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20water%20is%20pumped%20from%20the%20underground%20reserves%2C%20roughly%2093%25%20of%20that%20is%20used%20for%20these%20purposes.%20Ladakh%20is%20also%20shifting%20towards%20self-sufficiency%20in%20the%20food%20and%20crop%20market.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20also%20demands%20huge%20%5Bamounts%20of%5D%20water%2C%20and%20for%20that%2C%20people%20drill%20wells.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20pumped%20groundwater%20is%20nearly%207%25%2C%20used%20in%20crop%20fields%2C%20greenhouse%20vegetation%20cropping%2C%20fruits%2C%20and%20other%20crops%20not%20earlier%20grown%20in%20the%20region.%20Groundwater%20is%20also%20pumped%20by%20the%20hotel%20and%20guesthouse%20owners%20as%20they%20require%20fresh%20water%20for%20the%20tourists%20round%20the%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20920px)%20100vw%2C%20920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-groundwater-2-Reach-Ladakh-1726237897.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20growing%20demand%20for%20water%20in%20Leh%20requires%20better%20solutions.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2F