0a%20natural%20pond%20that%20harvests%20around%2030%2C000%20litres%20of%20rainwater.%20The%20same%20is%20channelled%20for%20irrigation%20purposes%20and%20vegetation.%20We%20encourage%20guests%20to%20harvest%20their%20own%20food%20and%20send%20it%20to%20the%20kitchen%20where%20Laali%20%3Cem%3Ebhabhi%20%3C%2Fem%3Euses%20it%20in%20the%20meals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20it%20is%20the%20creative%2C%20fine-tuned%20movements%20of%20the%20artists%20or%20the%20way%20Laali%20%3Cem%3Ebhabhi%20%3C%2Fem%3Emakes%20a%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20even%20the%20way%20Coco%20seems%20to%20mingle%20with%20the%20guests%20%E2%80%94%20Sankalp%20was%20right%20when%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20has%20a%20touch%20of%20art%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBook%20your%20creative%20escape%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vinyasa.earth%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20Sankalp%20Sharma%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726128139000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Frajasthani-food-1725901544.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D365250%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Founded%20by%20dancer%20Sankalp%20Sharma%2C%20Vinyasa%20Earth%20is%20a%20sustainable%20homestay%20in%20Jaipur%E2%80%99s%20Maheshwas%20Khurd%20Village.%20Built%20without%20cement%2C%20using%20only%20bamboo%2C%20mud%2C%20and%20lime%2C%20it%20offers%20artist%20residencies.%20With%20a%20focus%20on%20creativity%2C%20the%20homestay%20blends%20eco-conscious%20living%2C%20traditional%20Rajasthani%20meals%2C%20and%20artistic%20expression%20in%20a%20peaceful%20environment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365250%2Fvinyasa-earth-sankalp-sharma-sustainable-homestay-jaipur-artist-residencies-mud-bamboo-cob-lime%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Food%20Startup%20%E2%80%98Tocco%E2%80%99%20Helps%20People%20in%20Their%2050s%20Build%20an%20Identity%20Through%20Cooking%2C%20Earns%20Rs%201%20Cr%2FYr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20paid%20for%20my%20own%20trip%20and%20went%20to%20Dubai!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20platform%20helped%20me%20build%20my%20identity.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20very%20confident%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20menopause%2C%20staying%20busy%20is%20crucial%20to%20keep%20mood%20swings%20at%20bay.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20chefs%20of%20Tocco%2C%20an%20e-commerce%20platform%20that%20curates%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359581%2Finspiring-senior-citizens-india-running-successful-startups-isro-restaurants-oil-business-daycares%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome-cooked%20specialties%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20From%20Uma%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20prawn%20pickles%20in%20Kerala%20to%20Bhavana%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Enankhatais%20%3C%2Fem%3E(biscuits)%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Annie%20Philip%E2%80%99s%20matured%20plum%20cake%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Tocco%20is%20a%20melting%20pot%20of%20regional%20delicacies!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20women%20can%20be%20found%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20you%20just%20need%20to%20look%20and%20spend%20a%20few%20minutes%20talking%20to%20them.%20Ask%20your%20mother%20or%20aunt%20about%20their%20wishes%2C%20and%20if%20they%20are%20anything%20like%20Bhavana%20or%20Uma%2C%20they%20would%20have%20definitely%20harboured%20dreams%20of%20creating%20their%20own%20identity%20through%20cooking.%20Tocco%20makes%20it%20easy%20for%20neighbourhood%20home%20chefs%20to%20do%20just%20that%2C%20without%20the%20hassle%20of%20branding%20or%20marketing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20for%20this%20platform%20was%20born%20from%20founder%20Reshma%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20own%20desire%20to%20experience%20the%20taste%20of%20home%20while%20living%20away.%20After%20moving%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20work%2C%20she%20found%20herself%20caught%20in%20the%20cycle%20of%20eating%20outside%2C%20always%20craving%20her%20%3Cem%3Eamma%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20tasty%20food.%20Realising%20she%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20one%20looking%20for%20authentic%20Kerala%20food%2C%20she%20started%20making%20banana%20chips%20and%20selling%20them%20through%20her%20brand%2C%20%E2%80%98MeenGurry%20Memories%E2%80%99%2C%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacking%20memories%20of%20her%20%3Cem%3Eamma%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eammamma%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmother%E2%80%99s)%20generations-old%20recipe%20for%20the%20perfect%2C%20thin%2C%20and%20crispy%20banana%20chips%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20game-changer%20for%20Reshma%2C%20who%20was%20then%20working%20at%20an%20AI%2Fhealthcare%20startup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tocco%20chef%20Annie%20baking%20a%20plum%20cake.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-172603