re%20to%20get%20your%20fill%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Not%20just%20one%2C%20but%20an%20eclectic%20mix%20of%2024%20varieties%20will%20find%20their%20way%20to%20your%20doorstep%20if%20you%20wish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20brainwave%20by%20four%20childhood%20friends%20is%20making%20this%20possible.%20Their%20startup%20Fulva%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Kerala-based%20brand%20serving%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F286270%2Fmom-sells-authentic-maharashtrian-food-in-mumbai-pune-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthentic%20traditional%20food%20products%20%3C%2Fa%3Esourced%20from%20small-scale%20producers%20%E2%80%94%20is%20completing%20a%20year%20of%20operations%20and%20has%20already%20touched%20a%20milestone%20with%20a%20Rs%2084%20lakh%20turnover.%20And%20as%20they%20share%2C%20their%20success%20story%20is%20written%20by%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESquare-shaped%20pieces%20of%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20visited%20Kozhikode%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20know%20it%20is%20almost%20a%20sacrilege%20to%20not%20return%20home%20with%20servings%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20also%20considered%20a%20%E2%80%98prestige%20symbol%E2%80%99%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20history%20tells%20us%2C%20has%20an%20interesting%20story%20that%20prequels%20its%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20supposedly%20an%20Arab%20invention%20born%20around%20the%2016th%20century%20when%20the%20community%20settled%20in%20Kerala.%20They%20were%20intent%20on%20gifting%20a%20piece%20of%20their%20culinary%20prowess%20to%20Kozhikode%E2%80%99s%20Zamorin%20(monarch).%20And%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Emade%20the%20cut.%20It%20went%20on%20to%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20spice%20trade%20and%20eventually%20part%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20gastronomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20have%20been%20perplexed%20as%20to%20how%20a%20simple%20blend%20of%20water%2C%20sugar%2C%20corn%20starch%2C%20coconut%20oil%2C%20citrus%20salt%2C%20and%20flavourings%20birthed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F281110%2Fmithai-map-of-india-10-lesser-known-indian-sweets-you-must-try-at-least-once%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20dessert%20so%20exquisite%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20no%20successor%20dessert%20could%20compete%20with.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20said%20that%20no%20two%20blocks%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20the%20same%20as%20the%20ratio%20of%20each%20ingredient%20varies%20from%20proprietor%20to%20proprietor%20in%20Kozhikode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20tourists%20and%20locals%20aren%E2%80%99t%20picky%20about%20these%20changing%20nuances%20so%20long%20as%20they%20get%20their%20fill%20of%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20combo%20box%2C%20that%20features%2012%20premium%20varieties%20of%20Kozhikoden%20halwa%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364550%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20combos%20features%2012%20premium%20varieties%20of%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20was%20the%20case%20with%20four%20childhood%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Shabas%20Ahamed%20N%20C%2C%20Sanu%20Muhammed%20C%2C%20Irfan%20Safar%20S%2C%20and%20Thesreef%20Ali%20P%20K.%20Growing%20up%2C%20they%20gorged%20on%20the%20sweet%20treat.%20They%20considered%20it%20a%20usual%20feast.%20But%2C%20it%20was%20only%20when%20they%20moved%20out%20of%20their%20hometown%20to%20study%2C%20that%20they%20realised%20they%20were%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20friends%2C%20who%20were%20studying%20in%20different%20colleges%20in%20Kerala%2C%20were%20berated%20with%20similar%20requests%20on%20each%20trip%20back%20home.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EEnikk%20kurach%20Kozhikoden%20halwa%20venam%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Get%20me%20some%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa)%3C%2Fem%3E!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20request%20came%20from%20teachers%2C%20friends%20and%20hostel%20mates.%20And%20so%20on%20every%20return%20trip%2C%20the%20boys%20would%20return%20loaded%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F210948%2Ffood-history-origin-of-halwa-ceremony-budget-indian-desserts-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecolourful%20squares%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20were%20relished%20by%20its%20patrons.%20One%20day%2C%20the%20pattern%20was%20discussed%20over%20some%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20biscuits.%20They%20realised%20that%20people%20beyond%20Kozhikode%20and%20Kerala%20found%20profound%20delight%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20conversation%20furthered%2C%20it%20dawned%20on%20the%20four%20that%20while%20each%20had%20grown%20up%20eating%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20preference%20for%20flavour